<h2 lang="en-US" class="western">Catalan</h2>
<p><span lang="en-US">The Catalan people are considered to be the
native population of </span><span lang="en-US"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Principality_of_Catalonia">Catalonia</a>.</span></p>
